title: Intel Extension for TensorFlow
description: Intel® Extension for TensorFlow* is a heterogeneous, high performance deep learning extension plugin based on TensorFlow PluggableDevice interface to bring Intel XPU(GPU, CPU, etc) devices into TensorFlow open source community for AI workload acceleration. It allows flexibly plugging an XPU into TensorFlow on-demand, and exposing computing power inside Intel's hardware.
